            "text": "Chicago - Travel With Me & Baby"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " guide. If you are planning to travel to Chicago (with or without a baby!), I suggest taking advantage of the free upgrade right now! Just click on the link and it will direct you to a page where you can download and upgrade this guide (once you've already downloaded the app), or you can search for it in the app once you've downloaded it. I've noticed that on iPhone, the link will always direct you to the app store, even if you have already downloaded the app, so I recommend just searching in the app. The company has told me that this is an iPhone limitation."
